{"name":"Streamline a routine task with HTTP / REST API and Notion on autopilot","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"weeks","triggerAtDay":[1],"triggerAtHour":9}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"0eed47b8-d745-40b1-9fee-f6e4cd398ceb","name":"Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"6004ea92-8e8c-41a1-92b0-60e173b86dd0","name":"docId","value":"={{ $json.body?.docId || $json.body?.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"fafd1130-495d-4ecb-b2e6-a56596781ecc","name":"kind","value":"={{ $json.body?.type || 'default' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"fa74fd60-29cc-498e-b5bf-65702a8d2346","name":"payload","value":"={{ JSON.stringify($json.body || $json) }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"91cb012c-e4c0-48c1-aa37-ba33517d3c51","name":"Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"9648d23d-712f-4f51-a3d9-0bf7507e3e5f","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"job.start","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"job.start"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"39242a2e-21cc-48e2-afcf-5b061324977f","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"job.done","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"job.done"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"da62f8e0-44fd-4037-90ec-5758b8e274dd","name":"Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Database"},"title":"={{ $json.content || $json.docId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[702,130],"id":"5b6f1870-11f8-4d94-a6e2-c52d4c8a6a0d","name":"Handle 'job.start' → Notion","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"method":"POST","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/documents","sendBody":true,"specifyBody":"json","jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{"timeout":20000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1026,640],"id":"b213058b-90d7-4f40-aa0d-3a1aad913de4","name":"Handle 'job.done' → Forward API","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Database"},"title":"={{ $json.content || $json.docId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1350,1150],"id":"a0a70a73-61dd-418e-a7c4-542f53824863","name":"Log Unrecognized Kind","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1998,400],"id":"f9a1e0c1-219d-4c31-8e29-c698caa5bd76","name":"Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[2970,400],"id":"854daf79-371c-4d54-9a71-88b72e09dbf2","name":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[3294,400],"id":"69a7449f-493b-473f-a7c1-c8bc9f8d87cb","name":"Archive Row Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.content }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[3618,400],"id":"fb83abc1-e076-4bd4-b7f1-7e0109a33179","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"0cf32b53-bbd0-4114-9b6e-4cba245b2b20","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"9a2bc6b3-0e1a-4586-b90c-6a9e0b9fa0d0","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3942,400],"id":"a381c6b6-d65a-400f-87c8-6ecb7affc4f1","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[4266,400],"id":"1cf11b8a-53c0-4da9-b96c-7752b50ccc1d","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[4590,400],"id":"54ec28f2-d558-4472-8478-bd28b1ac4c1a","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"getAll","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Database"},"returnAll":true,"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[4914,400],"id":"1efc5fe5-d630-4b1f-b17b-4995b2591c50","name":"Load Previous Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\nconst current = $input.first().json;\nconst prev = $('Load Previous Snapshot').first().json || {};\nconst drift = {};\nfor (const k of Object.keys(current)) {\n  if (typeof current[k] === 'number' && typeof prev[k] === 'number' && prev[k] !== 0) {\n    drift[k] = Math.round(((current[k] - prev[k]) / prev[k]) * 1000) / 10;\n  }\n}\nreturn [{ json: { ...current, driftPct: drift, hasDrift: Object.values(drift).some(v => Math.abs(v) > 10) } }];"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[5238,400],"id":"779ab5b4-f5ff-42eb-b31b-acea671f1942","name":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Build a stable idempotency key per document (djb2 hash, no deps)\nfunction hash(s) {\n  let h = 5381;\n  for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) h = ((h << 5) + h + s.charCodeAt(i)) >>> 0;\n  return h.toString(16);\n}\nreturn $input.all().map(item => {\n  const j = item.json;\n  return { json: { ...j, idempotencyKey: hash([j.docId, j.content].join('|')) } };\n});"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[5562,400],"id":"7d91c28c-eebd-460d-826f-8fddc3d66c31","name":"Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"operation":"removeItemsSeenInPreviousExecutions","logic":"removeItemsWithAlreadySeenKeyValues","dedupeValue":"={{ $json.idempotencyKey }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.removeDuplicates","typeVersion":2,"position":[5886,400],"id":"e0cd3126-d315-46e5-ba49-5c097385ffd0","name":"Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"8ebdd477-c99e-4cb8-82f1-39f578e3d39a","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"cd2bf6f5-c15a-4860-b80a-a42ef6b94e3f","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"7445c76c-162b-4215-a18e-7780fabcf8aa","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,400],"id":"4ba32660-70ab-4e36-90a1-91f27bffa71e","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Database"},"title":"={{ $json.content || $json.docId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[6534,400],"id":"51ccb2a6-f4a4-480c-aa9e-6699c8204ac0","name":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"chatId":"={{ $json.chatId || 'OPS_CHAT_ID' }}","text":"=✅ Streamline a routine task with HTTP / REST API and Notion on autopilot — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","additionalFields":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.telegram","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[6858,400],"id":"f87e418b-e581-42cf-a818-4e79940c378b","name":"Send Summary to Telegram","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"60346e5f-56a7-4215-92d7-151ca92f681d","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"9d1d370c-0b34-457d-adf5-9f5bb69f2478","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"11852bfa-5eb3-4628-9f1c-d2f6bd8bbc2d","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,1420],"id":"1b666026-3c0a-44dc-ae8b-ef8fc979aa3a","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#ai-ops","cachedResultName":"#ai-ops"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[6534,1420],"id":"c370ae92-7388-4a0c-8b9b-0be6e57079f0","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Database"},"title":"={{ $json.content || $json.docId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[6858,1420],"id":"4e7e62cf-b34f-4478-a053-bb1019193ce7","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"5775a804-bbad-28a3-f9d4-8e66591213d0","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Map to Canonical Schema\n\nShapes the item: writes `docId`, `kind`, `payload`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Route by Event Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"3addab85-5bda-6248-00eb-1c3db59d3910","name":"Note: Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: job.start, job.done + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'job.start' → Notion · ②→ Handle 'job.done' → Forward API · ③→ Log Unrecognized Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0edbd2ad-bfeb-caf1-4216-00fa83cad4ef","name":"Note: Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'job.start' → Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"6a131fbf-9dd5-4052-1a55-1450eecdc19f","name":"Note: Handle 'job.start' → Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'job.done' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/documents — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"7c9a0932-046d-ad9f-d604-93d717a14659","name":"Note: Handle 'job.done' → Forward API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Unrecognized Kind\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"484e819c-f5d9-fbfd-8ed0-25c9546b75ee","name":"Note: Log Unrecognized Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Consolidate Handling\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"fedba834-4b0f-9871-d125-45d08a7f5b80","name":"Note: Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"d678976d-112f-590a-b25e-c7dd406e6703","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"7790e828-e3bb-17f7-3510-74892f4b54ec","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"bc51085a-4aaf-7fd2-0aac-bfbd2df3fa1a","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"77c78a63-6877-ee58-64cb-0bc2760a470c","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"0844aa02-06e9-e248-b4e8-48636a64cdbd","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"4e30e63d-a113-e95d-ae41-05ca92691789","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"7b1d8eb3-c004-44b5-5068-94f54b61e04b","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"8b6bc03f-87e8-8ef1-1f36-cc6b24c35bdb","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per document (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"e80bdf63-7386-4d5e-7336-f2bb735fdb82","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"f295246f-35f8-3fc8-5aad-4cf7ae20b390","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"0e0f52b7-d3fb-8d54-a34a-a951145c847a","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"0eabb4a8-bbcb-685b-7f62-62bead97486c","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"9cf16e91-6f24-b05c-a9ec-0e950fd87d30","name":"Note: Send Summary to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"17eed51f-3a50-da5c-1d8d-4ae4d0c57a6b","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"c20afa9f-18e5-9aca-4e6d-5db2eeaca943","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"b667c2a6-daee-f39d-59eb-8648f6d1e58b","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Streamline a routine task with HTTP / REST API and Notion on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** Workflow Automation · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nStreamline a routine task with HTTP / REST API and Notion on autopilot. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual ai pipelines is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'job.start' → Notion → Consolidate Handling → Serialize Run Output (CSV) → Archive Row Snapshot → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to workflow automation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating ai pipelines in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"205b0a20-53ed-2f44-f391-18bf079caf88","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"ac0613b5-454b-13b8-1106-c1dd3bedbdd4","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"72b29744-67e0-658d-a350-fb2960442438","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your ai pipelines process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-290],"id":"43f22e3a-ca0c-978d-b8dc-ee5e2ffc044e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Map to Canonical Schema","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Map to Canonical Schema":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Handle 'job.start' → Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'job.done' → Forward API","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Unrecognized Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'job.start' → Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'job.done' → Forward API":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Log Unrecognized Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Consolidate Handling":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Telegram":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"ea060385-e1f5-4aa2-9441-3aa1154169cb","id":"FDX10427"}